														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4111825">
									

<p>This is a beautiful echo of the tale that started it all, a beautiful tale of death in a world longing for it, and a wonderful ending to this chapter in the end of death story.</p>
<p>But the beautiful (and ugly) thing about End of Death is how it will never end. Ever.</p>

