			<div class="content" id="post-content-4144650">
									

<p>Where to even begin with this?</p>
<p>Everything about this canon is amazing from the creative concept to its frankly beautiful description of death. This series has opened my eyes to something that I've never truly experience from fiction, it has changed my view on life and death for the better, and it has inspired me to truly appreciate the world for what it is.</p>
<p>Thank you to everyone involved with the creation, writing, and critiquing of this series. I hope all of you enjoyed this as much as I did.</p>

